{"tid":1014974,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"西醫話我個胃唔好","createTime":"2019-02-09T15:21:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-09T16:48:03.000Z","uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"28c15fef3f8939468001b11f8dc98a8cde43a035","tid":1014974,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T15:21:04.000Z","msg":"唔舒服去睇醫生（唔係腸胃唔舒服）<br />\n有2-3個醫生都係 examine左一陣 <br />\n話我個胃唔係幾好 開埋胃藥俾我<br />\n但佢地淨係用左聽筒聽下個肺<br />\n有個把埋脈 （以為中醫先會）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人都係咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPs 我係有時會胃氣脹住/胃酸到流咁<br />\n有一排全日唔駛點食野都覺得唔肚餓"},{"pid":"c03607ba2b63182d5b7c41a247e969e46dda6a97","tid":1014974,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T16:29:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35ae20d13a37c7368be93e86769639e32c83debd","tid":1014974,"uid":202456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T16:32:18.000Z","msg":"睇開個西醫次次都把脈<br />\n開聲問先知係數緊脈搏唔係中醫個種<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15a81e395153c6145442e5f313f65c25165c8089","tid":1014974,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35ae20d13a37c7368be93e86769639e32c83debd","tid":1014974,"uid":202456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T16:32:18.000Z","msg":"睇開個西醫次次都把脈<br />\n開聲問先知係數緊脈搏唔係中醫個種<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T16:48:03.000Z","msg":"原來係咁<br />\n個醫生把完脈話我胃唔好<br />\n仲以為係中醫咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}